verbs.description: A federal judge [V: is] weighing a crucial decision over who will be tasked with reviewing the materials that were seized from Michael Cohen , President Trump 's longtime personal attorney . Attorneys for Cohen and Trump have pushed for the appointment of a so - called special master , a neutral third party who would decide what materials are covered by attorney - client privilege and can not be given to prosecutors .
